===生物正交性===
尽管叠氮化物不是活性最高的[[1,3-偶极体|1,3-偶极体]]，但其具有分子小、在新陈代谢过程中保持稳定、不是天然存在于生物体中，因此是一种极好的生物正交官能团。<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1021/jo00865a001|title = 1,3-Dipolar cycloadditions. 76. Concerted nature of 1,3-dipolar cycloadditions and the question of diradical intermediates|year = 1976|last1 = Huisgen|first1 = Rolf.|journal = The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume = 41|issue = 3|pages = 403}}</ref> 

[[炔基|炔基]]虽没有叠氮基团那么小，但也具有稳定性和生物正交性，常用于[[In_vivo|活体内]]标记。<ref name="Doija">{{cite journal|doi = 10.1021/ja9003624|title = Reactivity and Regioselectivity in 1,3-Dipolar Cycloadditions of Azides to Strained Alkynes and Alkenes: A Computational Study|year = 2009|last1 = Schoenebeck|first1 = Franziska|last2 = Ess|first2 = Daniel H.|last3 = Jones|first3 = Gavin O.|last4 = Houk|first4 = K. N.|journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume = 131|issue = 23|pages = 8121–33|pmid = 19459632}}</ref>

